{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01T8NSdemKV2G9sVnYm2RqWp","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→artifact: spec\n     3→loop: 1\n     4→project: ralph-burning-rewrite\n     5→backend: claude(opus)\n     6→role: planner\n     7→created_at: 2026-03-11T17:50:55Z\n     8→---\n     9→\n    10→# Feature: Foundation — Domain Model, Workspace Init, and Flow Discovery\n    11→\n    12→## Description\n    13→Bootstrap the `ralph-burning` Rust binary crate with the v1 domain model, workspace initialization, and flow discovery CLI commands. This is delivery roadmap slice 1: it establishes the Cargo project, bounded-context folder skeleton, core domain types, the `ralph-burning init` command that creates a `.ralph-burning/` workspace, and `flow list` / `flow show` commands that enumerate the four built-in flow presets with their stage sequences. It also seeds the conformance test harness with initial Gherkin scenario IDs covering workspace init and flow discovery.\n    14→\n    15→## Acceptance Criteria\n    16→- [ ] `ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml` compiles a binary named `ralph-burning` (edition 2021, Rust stable)\n    17→- [ ] Dependencies include at minimum: `clap` (derive), `serde`/`serde_json`, `toml`/`toml_edit`, `thiserror`, `chrono`, and `tokio` (rt-multi-thread)\n    18→- [ ] Source tree contains the bounded-context folder skeleton: `src/contexts/{workspace_governance, project_run_record, workflow_composition, agent_execution, requirements_drafting, automation_runtime, conformance_spec}/mod.rs` plus `src/adapters/mod.rs` and `src/shared/mod.rs`\n    19→- [ ] Domain model types defined in `src/shared/domain.rs` (or equivalent shared module): `FlowPreset` enum (`Standard`, `QuickDev`, `DocsChange`, `CiImprovement`), `StageId` enum with all stages from all four presets, `StageCursor` struct (stage, cycle, attempt, completion_round), `ProjectId`, `RunId`, `WorkspaceConfig` struct\n    20→- [ ] Four built-in flow presets are defined in `src/contexts/workflow_composition/` with their exact stage sequences as specified in the master prompt section 9\n    21→- [ ] `ralph-burning init` creates `.ralph-burning/workspace.toml` with sensible defaults (version field, created timestamp) and the required subdirectory stubs (`projects/`, `requirements/`, `daemon/tasks/`, `daemon/leases/`)\n    22→- [ ] `ralph-burning init` on an already-initialized workspace prints an error message and exits non-zero (no implicit re-init)\n    23→- [ ] `ralph-burning flow list` prints all four preset names with a short description\n    24→- [ ] `ralph-burning flow show <flow-id>` prints the ordered stage list, validation profile defaults (final review enabled/disabled), and stage count for the given preset\n    25→- [ ] `ralph-burning flow show` with an invalid flow-id exits non-zero with a clear error\n    26→- [ ] CLI top-level uses `clap` subcommand routing with placeholder subcommand stubs for all v1 commands (config, project, run, requirements, daemon, conformance) that print \"not yet implemented\" and exit non-zero\n    27→- [ ] `tests/conformance/features/workspace_init.feature` contains Gherkin scenarios: init fresh workspace, init already-initialized workspace, init verifies directory structure\n    28→- [ ] `tests/conformance/features/flow_discovery.feature` contains Gherkin scenarios: list all presets, show each preset, show invalid preset\n    29→- [ ] Unit tests exist for: flow preset stage ordering, stage cursor construction invariants (monotonic cycle/completion round), workspace config serialization round-trip\n    30→- [ ] `cargo build` succeeds with no warnings; `cargo test` passes all tests\n    31→- [ ] `cargo clippy` reports no warnings\n    32→\n    33→## Files to Modify/Create\n    34→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml` — new crate manifest with binary target and dependencies\n    35→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/main.rs` — async entry point, tracing init, clap CLI dispatch\n    36→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/lib.rs` — public module re-exports\n    37→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/mod.rs` — top-level clap `Cli` struct with all subcommand groups (stubs for unimplemented ones)\n    38→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/init.rs` — `ralph-burning init` implementation\n    39→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/flow.rs` — `ralph-burning flow list` and `flow show` implementation\n    40→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/config.rs` — placeholder stub\n    41→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/project.rs` — placeholder stub\n    42→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/run.rs` — placeholder stub\n    43→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/requirements.rs` — placeholder stub\n    44→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs` — placeholder stub\n    45→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/conformance.rs` — placeholder stub\n    46→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/mod.rs` — shared module root\n    47→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/domain.rs` — core domain types (FlowPreset, StageId, StageCursor, ProjectId, RunId, WorkspaceConfig)\n    48→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/error.rs` — shared error types using `thiserror`\n    49→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/workspace_governance/mod.rs` — workspace init logic, config loading, workspace version check\n    50→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/workflow_composition/mod.rs` — flow preset registry, stage sequence definitions\n    51→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/project_run_record/mod.rs` — module stub\n    52→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/mod.rs` — module stub\n    53→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/requirements_drafting/mod.rs` — module stub\n    54→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/mod.rs` — module stub\n    55→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/conformance_spec/mod.rs` — module stub\n    56→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/mod.rs` — adapter module stub\n    57→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/fs.rs` — filesystem adapter for workspace creation (ports/adapters boundary)\n    58→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/workspace_init.feature` — Gherkin scenarios for init\n    59→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/flow_discovery.feature` — Gherkin scenarios for flow commands\n    60→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/domain_test.rs` — unit tests for domain types\n    61→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/flow_preset_test.rs` — unit tests for flow preset definitions\n    62→- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/workspace_test.rs` — unit tests for workspace config serialization\n    63→\n    64→## Dependencies\n    65→- Requires: none (first slice)\n    66→- Blocks: slice 2 (flow preset definitions + stage contracts + renderer contracts), slice 3 (workspace governance effective config), slice 4 (project/run canonical store)\n    67→\n    68→---\n    69→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Gx1iRbRieStJESk4vaaNVA","session_id":"68f65612-956d-4383-9b3f-2ff2c684a050","uuid":"6bd33c54-48f3-4171-a9fd-55dbb83d448f"}
